<h>'s newsletter is sent out monthly (or so) by our webmaster
Deirdre, and includes information on our newest zones, quests
and other special topics.  

Sign up for the newsletter on our website:
     http://www.sneezymud.com

Email addresses collected for the newsletter will only be used
to send the monthly newsletter, special quest bulletins to alert 
players to a special quest in progress or to inform players of
an extended MUD outage.  You may also choose to sign up for 
maintenance alerts regarding scheduled downtime.  


